    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-07-01T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-07-01T17:00:00-05:00" n="65"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d65">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.51/998: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-01T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >July 1, 1931—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 9:09 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>91. Department’s 47, June 26, 7 p.m. Four millions made available to the
                    Government yesterday; actually in their hands today.</p>
                <p>Outstanding credits renewed for 90 days at 7 percent with the understanding that
                    increased rate of interest or payment of expenses will be taken up again
                    September 30.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
